---

## What I added and why:

| Addition | Why |
|---|---|
| `.env.*` | Catches `.env.local`, `.env.production` etc |
| `npm-debug.log*` | Catches all npm log variants |
| `.vscode/` | Hides your editor settings |
| `Thumbs.db` | Windows OS file |
| `coverage/` | Test coverage reports |

